{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_013YqsysTuNap98uPzCGzsFf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_0166jw9oa1w6nSq3vJX6KTbo","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/mydata/karma/runs/long-rerun/mongodb-long-all-cases-marathon-a-20260618_155709/stages/stage_07/submit.txt","content":"MongoDB server TLS certificate rotation — completed without downtime.\n\nWHAT WAS DONE\n1. Extracted the existing CA cert+key from secret `mongodb-tls-ca` (CN=mongo-ca,\n   valid 2026..2036). The CA was left completely UNCHANGED (verified byte-identical\n   before and after).\n2. Generated a brand-new server private key and CSR, then signed a new server\n   certificate with the EXISTING CA, valid for 1 year (notBefore Jun 18 2026 →\n   notAfter Jun 18 2027). Preserved subject CN=mongo-rs and all original SANs\n   (localhost, mongo, mongo.mongodb[.svc[.cluster.local]], and the three\n   mongo-rs-{0,1,2}.mongo.mongodb.svc.cluster.local pod hostnames), plus\n   serverAuth/clientAuth EKU.\n3. Updated secret `mongodb-tls-cert` (key `server.pem` = new cert + new key).\n4. Rolled the StatefulSet `mongo-rs` one pod at a time (`kubectl rollout restart`\n   + `rollout status`) so the 3-member replica set stayed available throughout —\n   no downtime.\n\nVERIFICATION\n- CA secret (ca.crt and ca.key) byte-identical to pre-rotation: trust unchanged.\n- `openssl verify -CAfile ca.crt new-server.crt` → OK.\n- Live TLS handshake against all 3 replicas (s_client with the CA) →\n  \"Verify return code: 0 (ok)\", subject CN=mongo-rs, new 1-year validity.\n- Replica set healthy over TLS: mongo-rs-2 PRIMARY, mongo-rs-0/1 SECONDARY.\n\nThe old server cert (expiring Jun 20 2026, ~2 days) has been replaced by a cert\nvalid ~1 year, signed by the same CA, with zero service interruption.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":310,"cache_creation_input_tokens":506,"cache_read_input_tokens":46621,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":506},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"712f989c-5366-444b-b7bb-1031be4e0285","uuid":"9abf492a-8911-454a-b3fc-9c596b6c2aec","request_id":"req_011CcB3BcUTTAa6FiPojHM2w"}
